{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a sci-fi space strategy combat game where players can devise battle strategies and assign specific ships, which can be customized with modules according to player configurations. The game features an open-ended storyline with optional side missions that players can freely choose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Subsequent updates or DLCs for the game, based on its popularity, will broadly include the following content:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Level System</strong>: Additional levels will be introduced.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Character System</strong>: Characters will have a dedicated character interface. This includes illustrations, detailed background stories, special skills or abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Weapon System</strong>: More weapons and equipment will be added.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ship System</strong>: Additional ships will be introduced.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Long-term Vision</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>City System</strong>: This may require a substantial amount of time and effort.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sovereignty System</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Economic and Trade System</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Others</strong>: Random items, blueprint crafting, spaceship production, alien creatures, among other things.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434150/extras/BattleRoom1.jpg?t=1737536315\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434150/extras/Battle2.jpg?t=1737536315\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434150/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=173